{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place oil, garlic and shallots in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 3<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then sauté <b>5 min\/100°C\/speed <b>.","Add chilli, cumin seeds, curry powder and turmeric then fry <b>2 min\/100°C\/speed <b>.","Add water, vegetable stock and tomato purée then heat <b>5 min\/98°C\/speed <b>.","Add sweet potatoes and broccoli then, with simmering basket in place of measuring cup, simmer <b>10 min\/98°C\/\/speed 0.5<b> until sweet potato is tender.","Season to taste, sprinkle with coriander and serve with rice or Indian bread."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["2 Tbsp oil","2 garlic cloves","2 shallots, halved","½ - 1 red chilli, to taste, deseeded if desired","1 tsp cumin seeds","1 tsp curry powder","1 tsp ground turmeric","2 Tbsp tomato purée","200 g water","½ vegetable stock cube (for 0.5 l)","250 g sweet potatoes, peeled, diced (2-3 cm)","100 g broccoli, cut in florets (3-4 cm)","fine sea salt, to taste","ground black pepper, to taste","fresh coriander leaves, roughly chopped, to garnish"]}],"id":"r235756","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-7nLPiBUiMNI\/XZVQLfazXxI\/AAAAAAAAc-o\/GlDknyNZPeoZ98J6RhqyAEaBlzajWyaZACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_IfdverQPu-51qEZt.png","title":"Sweet Potato Curry","publishedAt":"2017-10-02T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"12 g","fat":"28 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"62 g","calories":"2428 kJ \/ 581 kcal"},"basicInfo":["easy","5m","30m","1 portion"]}